snippets.title: ContentService updateContent Sample
snippets.description: Update a content. Only supports full resource update.

snippets.title: ContentService deleteLake Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a lake resource. All zones within the lake must be deleted before the lake can be deleted.

snippets.title: ContentService listLakes Sample
snippets.description: Lists lake resources in a project and location.

snippets.title: ContentService listLakeActions Sample
snippets.description: Lists action resources in a lake.

snippets.title: ContentService createZone Sample
snippets.description: Creates a zone resource within a lake.

snippets.title: ContentService deleteZone Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a zone resource. All assets within a zone must be deleted before the zone can be deleted.

snippets.title: ContentService listZones Sample
snippets.description: Lists zone resources in a lake.

snippets.title: ContentService listZoneActions Sample
snippets.description: Lists action resources in a zone.

snippets.title: ContentService deleteAsset Sample
snippets.description: Deletes an asset resource. The referenced storage resource is detached (default) or deleted based on the associated Lifecycle policy.

snippets.title: ContentService listAssets Sample
snippets.description: Lists asset resources in a zone.

snippets.title: ContentService listAssetActions Sample
snippets.description: Lists action resources in an asset.

snippets.title: ContentService createTask Sample
snippets.description: Creates a task resource within a lake.

snippets.title: ContentService listTasks Sample
snippets.description: Lists tasks under the given lake.

snippets.title: ContentService listJobs Sample
snippets.description: Lists Jobs under the given task.

snippets.title: ContentService cancelJob Sample
snippets.description: Cancel jobs running for the task resource.

snippets.title: ContentService deleteEnvironment Sample
snippets.description: Delete the environment resource. All the child resources must have been deleted before environment deletion can be initiated.

snippets.title: ContentService listEnvironments Sample
snippets.description: Lists environments under the given lake.

snippets.title: ContentService listSessions Sample
snippets.description: Lists session resources in an environment.

snippets.title: ContentService updateEntity Sample
snippets.description: Update a metadata entity. Only supports full resource update.

snippets.title: ContentService listEntities Sample
snippets.description: List metadata entities in a zone.

snippets.title: ContentService getPartition Sample
snippets.description: Get a metadata partition of an entity.

snippets.title: ContentService listPartitions Sample
snippets.description: List metadata partitions of an entity.
